16namespace webrtc {
17
18EchoCanceller3Factory::EchoCanceller3Factory() {}
19
20EchoCanceller3Factory::EchoCanceller3Factory(const EchoCanceller3Config& config)
21 : config_(config) {}
22
23std::unique_ptr<EchoControl> EchoCanceller3Factory::Create(
24 int sample_rate_hz,
25 int num_render_channels,
26 int num_capture_channels) {
27 return std::make_unique<EchoCanceller3>(
28 config_, sample_rate_hz, num_render_channels, num_capture_channels);
29}
